Package uncc.objects

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Book
    Object that holds information about a book used in the tutoring center.
    HourRange
    Object that holds information about the hours in a day that a uncc.objects.Tutor object is available for tutoring, as stored by a uncc.objects.Timesheet object.
    HSQLDatabaseObject
    Abstract base class used to enforce object standards across Java objects that will be used to create tables in our database.
    ISBN
    ISBN object used to store ISBN-10 and ISBN-13 representations of a uncc.objects.Book object's ISBN.
    Rental
    Object that holds information about a book Rental.
    Student
    Object that holds information about a Student.
    Timesheet
    Object used to store a Tutor's availability.
    Tutor
    Object used to store information about a Tutor, their schedule, and their course expertise.
